    funFact: 'Lavash — Armenia\'s paper-thin flatbread baked on the walls of a clay tonir oven — was inscribed on UNESCO\'s Intangible Cultural Heritage list in 2014. The tradition of baking lavash is a communal, multigenerational ritual involving the whole household.',
