    funFact: 'Slovenian pumpkin seed oil — a dark, nutty oil pressed from roasted pumpkin seeds — has been produced in the Styria region for over 300 years and now holds EU Protected Designation of Origin status. It\'s drizzled on everything from salads to vanilla ice cream.',
