    funFact: 'The Viennese coffee house tradition — sitting for hours over a single coffee while reading newspapers — is UNESCO Intangible Cultural Heritage. Vienna\'s grand coffeehouses (Café Central, Café Hawelka) serve as second living rooms for locals who can nurse one Melange for an entire afternoon.',
