    funFact: 'Bulgarian rose oil (from the Rosa Damascena grown in the Valley of Roses near Kazanlak) is one of the world\'s most expensive commodities by weight — used in fine perfumery and Bulgariancooking alike. Bulgaria produces over 80% of the world\'s rose oil.',
