    funFact: 'Sarajevo\'s ćevabdžinica (ćevapi restaurant) culture is so serious that established restaurants like Ćevabdžinica Hodžić have been operating continuously for over 100 years. Sarajevo\'s ćevapi uses only beef — never pork — reflecting the city\'s Muslim majority heritage.',
