    funFact: 'Eswatini\'s King Mswati III is one of Africa\'s last absolute monarchs — and the royal Reed Dance (Umhlanga), where tens of thousands of Swazi maidens bring reeds to the queen mother, is accompanied by elaborate feasting and the serving of traditional Swazi foods and sorghum beer.',
