    description: 'Venezuelan cuisine is built around corn — arepas (corn flatbreads) are eaten at every meal and define Venezuelan food culture globally. The llanos (vast plains) produce exceptional beef; coastal fishing communities contribute fresh Caribbean seafood. Hallacas (corn tamales) are the Christmas centerpiece.',
